reviewText: Since this video was for my granddaughter, I can tell you that my daughter has the Aristocats ready to play at all times. I am told she loves this movie and it is one of her favorites!
As described. Received on time. Would buy from again. A+

This is a delightful movie. It is great for toddlers
as well. They love the cats, voices, songs and
animation. Older children can follow the story.
The children watched this over & over. It is good
family entertainment.
